<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(to right, #4f46e5, #6366f1);
        color: white;
        padding: 30px;
        border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .header h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 24px;
      }
      .content {
        background: #f9fafb;
        padding: 30px;
        border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        border-top: none;
      }
      .info-box {
        background: white;
        border-left: 4px solid #4f46e5;
        padding: 15px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        border-radius: 4px;
      }
      .info-row {
        display: flex;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      .info-label {
        font-weight: bold;
        width: 150px;
        color: #6b7280;
      }
      .info-value {
        color: #111827;
      }
      .status-badge {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 6px 12px;
        border-radius: 9999px;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 600;
        background: #fef3c7;
        color: #92400e;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 30px;
        padding-top: 20px;
        border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        color: #6b7280;
        font-size: 14px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="header">
      <h1>✓ Demande de congé soumise</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p>Bonjour <%= @employee.first_name %>,</p>

      <p>Votre demande de congé a bien été enregistrée et envoyée pour approbation.</p>

      <div class="info-box">
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Type de congé:</span>
          <span class="info-value"><%= @leave_request.leave_type_label %></span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Date de début:</span>
          <span class="info-value"><%= l(@leave_request.start_date, format: :long) %></span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Date de fin:</span>
          <span class="info-value"><%= l(@leave_request.end_date, format: :long) %></span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Nombre de jours:</span>
          <span class="info-value"><%= @leave_request.total_days %> jour(s)</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Statut:</span>
          <span class="info-value"><span class="status-badge">En attente</span></span>
        </div>
        <% if @leave_request.reason.present? %>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Motif:</span>
          <span class="info-value"><%= @leave_request.reason %></span>
        </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>

      <% if @manager.present? %>
      <p>Votre demande a été transmise à <strong><%= @manager.full_name %></strong> pour validation.</p>
      <% end %>

      <p>Vous recevrez une notification par email dès qu'une décision aura été prise.</p>

      <p>
        Cordialement,<br>
        <strong>L'équipe Izi-RH</strong>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>Cet email a été envoyé automatiquement, merci de ne pas y répondre.</p>
      <p>&copy; <%= Date.current.year %> Izi-RH. Tous droits réservés.</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
